com.hp.hpl.jena.update
Class UpdateAction

java.lang.Object
  com.hp.hpl.jena.update.UpdateAction

public class UpdateAction
extends java.lang.Object

A class of forms for executing SPARQL Update operations. parse* means the update request is in a string; read* means read the contents of a file.
